{"tid":594333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實SG Cheronna 先係最正","createTime":"2018-03-15T17:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T18:38:04.000Z","uid":53180,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c299d0f0182fc0ff08211e377036483d217c6794","tid":594333,"uid":53180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T17:53:25.000Z","msg":"Heidi依家係美容達人 無哂包包面 I.T老細係咁比job佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都係黃河果期最正<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/sYAtTYW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsYAtTYW.gif&h=36379b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYanny厚度呢就話佢係冰美人 但好多時都覺佢呆下呆下咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但自從佢ig單打heidi之後就覺得佢係西面人 <br />\n<img src=\"http://202.125.90.234/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20151018/photo/bkn-20151018070047859-1018_00862_001_06p.jpg?20151018073633\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F202.125.90.234%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20151018%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20151018070047859-1018_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20151018073633&h=4533ebee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAka幾正 諗起佢比偽毒欺騙感情就覺得慘慘豬 佢最近有個畫展做慈善 幾有愛心喎   <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.next.nextmedia.com/images/next-photos/NextMag/1450/640pixfolder/E1450_005_3959.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.next.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2FNextMag%2F1450%2F640pixfolder%2FE1450_005_3959.jpg&h=9097da04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有個好似叫Jessica 講都廢事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCheronna 有幾正唔使多講 雖然比被私有化左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sea1-1.cdninstagram.com/t51.2885-15/e35/14582393_522910157900059_7837407178724999168_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sea1-1.cdninstagram.com%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F14582393_522910157900059_7837407178724999168_n.jpg&h=741f7403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170423/photo/bkn-20170423151437510-0423_00862_001_07p.jpg?20170423160135\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170423%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170423151437510-0423_00862_001_07p.jpg%3F20170423160135&h=4a300b80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.jmen.com.hk/assets/images/JMEN/Others/J%20FEMME/femmea2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jmen.com.hk%2Fassets%2Fimages%2FJMEN%2FOthers%2FJ%2520FEMME%2Ffemmea2.jpg&h=96cf7280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喱排仲好fit 邊唱邊跳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CcjikcdZWd0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCcjikcdZWd0&d=XAG6UsVC1C%2FKdYYBU0ASQwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=bfa3ffd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CcjikcdZWd0</a>"},{"pid":"54e67eb68fd7e71e281f8ab90254f9f6518a6cea","tid":594333,"uid":33819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T17:55:53.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"acf375cceda3c3d923aa38593d6018e1ca92b8b7","tid":594333,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T18:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}